<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="renderer" content="webkit|ie-comp|ie-stand">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no" />
<meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-siteapp" />

<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/iconfont/iconfont.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/H-ui/H-ui.min.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/H-ui/H-ui.admin.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/H-ui/skin/skin.css" id="skin" />
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/H-ui/style.css" />

<title>我的桌面</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-container">
	<p class="f-20 text-success">英雄联盟</p>
	<p>以下是最新英雄联盟资讯</p>
	<table class="table table-border table-bordered table-bg">
		<thead>
			<tr>
				<th colspan="7" scope="col" style="text-align:center">信息统计</th>
			</tr>
			<tr class="text-c">
				<th>文章分类</th>
				<th>标题</th>
				<th>回复和浏览量</th>
				<th>发表时间</th>
				<th>采集时间</th>
				<th>全文链接</th>				
			</tr>
		</thead>
		<tbody>
			<% datas.forEach(function(data){%>
                <tr class="text-c">
                    <td><%=data.leftTag%></td>
                    <td style="text-align:left"><%=data.title%></td>
                    <td><%=data.backAndSee%></td>
                    <td><%=data.dateTime%></td>
                    <td><%=new Date((data.uploadTime) * 1000).toLocaleString().replace(new RegExp('/','g'),"-")%></td>
                    <td><a target="_parent" href='<%=data.articeUrl%>'><%=data.articeUrl%></a></td>								
                </tr>
			<% }) %>
		</tbody>
	</table>
	
	<div style="text-align:center;padding-top:10px;">
		<%if(page>0){%><a href="/page/wzry?page=<%=page-1%>&from=<%=from%>">上一页</a><%}else{%><span>上一页</span><%}%>
		<span>  |  </span>
		<%if(page<maxp-1){%><a href="/page/wzry?page=<%=page+1%>&from=<%=from%>">下一页</a><%}else{%><span>下一页</span><%}%>
	</div>
</div>
<footer class="footer mt-20">
  <div class="container">
    <p>本系统由<a href="" target="_blank" title="H-ui前端框架"> H-ui </a>提供技术支持<br>
	更多资讯请关注微博：游戏资讯整合平台<br>
	Copyright &copy;2018-2019. All Rights Reserved.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../js/jquery.min.js"></script> 
<script type="text/javascript" src="../js/H-ui.min.js"></script> 

</body>
</html>
